For this to work, you need the following to be used as a bookmarklet:

&lt;a href="javascript:var%20s=document.createElement("script");s.src="http://jsjohnst.github.com/flickr_video.js";document.body.appendChild(s);"&gt;FlickrVideo5&lt;/a&gt;

Replacing the s.src URL with the URL to your modified version of course. :)

